    lubridate (>= 1.9.3),
    methods (>= 4.4.1),
    R (>= 4.4.0),
    readr (>= 2.1.5),
    snakecase (>= 0.11.1),
    stringr (>= 1.5.1)
Imports: 
    utils
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
